OL,3,CShoreham air crash pilot applies to
OL,4,Cget flying licence back
OL,6,FThe pilot involved in the Shoreham
OL,7,FAirshow disaster is appealing against
OL,8,Fthe decision to revoke his flying
OL,9,Flicence.
OL,11,FAndrew Hill, 60, is appearing in front
OL,12,Fof a Civil Aviation Authority (CAA)
OL,13,Fpanel in London, according to a
OL,14,Fdocument published by the regulator.
OL,16,FEleven men were killed when Mr Hill
OL,17,Fcrashed into the A27 while performing
OL,18,Fa manoeuvre at the Shoreham Airshow in
OL,19,FWest Sussex on August 22, 2015.
