OL,3,CShoreham air crash pilot applies to
OL,4,Cget flying licence back
OL,6,FHis licence was suspended by the CAA
OL,7,Ffollowing the incident in a Hawker
OL,8,FHunter plane.
OL,10,FMr Hill was charged with 11 counts of
OL,11,Fmanslaughter by gross negligence but,
OL,12,Fafter a trial, was found not guilty in
OL,13,FMarch 2019.
OL,15,FWest Sussex senior coroner Penelope
OL,16,FSchofield ruled at an inquest in
OL,17,FDecember 2022 that his significant
OL,18,Ferrors and "poor" flying led to the 11
OL,19,Fmen being unlawfully killed.
