OL,3,CShoreham air crash pilot applies to
OL,4,Cget flying licence back
OL,6,FMr Hill is seeking the return of his
OL,7,Ffull pilot's licence.
OL,9,FThe two-day hearing at the
OL,10,FInternational Dispute Resolution
OL,11,FCentre in London began on Wednesday.
OL,13,FA decision is expected to be published
OL,14,Fup to 10 days after the hearing ends.
