OL,3,CShoreham air crash pilot applies to
OL,4,Cget flying licence back
OL,6,FWhen it emerged in December last year
OL,7,Fthat Mr Hill wanted to fly again,
OL,8,FAnthony Mallinson, whose father
OL,9,FGraham, 72, was killed in the Shoreham
OL,10,Fdisaster, told The Sun newspaper it
OL,11,Fwas causing "stress and worry" for the
OL,12,Fvictims' loved ones.
OL,14,FHe said: "We all, as a collaborative
OL,15,Fof families, feel extremely strongly
OL,16,Fthat he never has his pilot's licence
OL,17,Freinstated out of respect for all of
OL,18,Fus, the families and all of our loved
OL,19,Fones lost.
